                        <note rend="inline" type="source">711.60p2/33: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Minister in Latvia</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Coleman</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Riga</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-04-20T13:00:00+02:00"><hi rend="italic">April 20,
                                        1928—1 p.m.</hi></date><lb/>[Received April 20—9:45
                                a.m.]</dateline></opener>
                        <p>36. Department’s 24, April 18, 3 p.m. United States-Latvian treaty of
                            friendship, commerce and consular rights signed at noon today.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Coleman</hi></signed></closer>
